The Bafang 850C / DPC-14 display is a color display that is manufactured by http://aptdevelop.com/. You can buy  it on many online shops like Ebay, Aliexpress, PSWPower, etc.

This display works from 24V up to 52V (7S up to 14S) battery packs.

'''NOTE:''' There are different versions of Bafang 850C / DPC-14 display and the ones manufactured after the first quarter of 2018 should work with our flexible Open Source Firmware. Any Bafang 850C or DPC-14 purchased recently should work.<br>
Users that bought recently from [http://www.pswpower.com/ven.php?cargo.2016-5e-2eaj PSWPower shop, the model P850C on this link], reported that it works.